{"tid":993484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡男演員馮偉衷服兵役期間受重傷不治","createTime":"2019-01-24T03:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T12:02:23.000Z","uid":6497,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"847dfb716cc05584f0831e6c82582fbe9bf60ff6","tid":993484,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T03:12:49.000Z","msg":"新加坡男演員馮偉衷服兵役期間，本月19日在新西蘭演習時受重傷，延至昨晚不治。<br />\n<br />\n去年飾演他媽媽的葉全真凌晨發文哀悼：「天使，謝謝你來走了一遭，留下了屬於真、善與美的樣貌。你曾説過，去的國家不多，帶著你的微笑，展開你的翅膀，翱翔吧！」<br />\n<br />\n新加坡國防部表示，現年28歲的一等中士戰備軍人馮偉衷，本月初到新西蘭懷烏魯訓練區參加演練，上周末維修155毫米榴彈炮車時被意外壓傷胸腹，由直升機送往醫院搶救，情況一度好轉。其後，新加坡國防部長黃永宏其後透露，馮偉衷做了第三次手術後，仍情況危急，轉入加護病房，靠儀器維持心肺和腎臟功能，延至深夜宣告不治。<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/1/1548290292_xE-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F1%2F1548290292_xE-1280w.jpg&h=a938f38d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20553087d824ca53b29eef2ec3ab3ce9a6720d37","tid":993484,"uid":67500,"like":5,"dislike":39,"score":-34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T03:14:16.000Z","msg":"正宗得個樣"},{"pid":"317e6c3555092944fd0149e9127269ca08151321","tid":993484,"uid":232028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T03:16:50.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"d4872eb0dcecfe309bcf8a8da33cd18a6da34b9f","tid":993484,"uid":131259,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"quote":{"pid":"20553087d824ca53b29eef2ec3ab3ce9a6720d37","tid":993484,"uid":67500,"like":5,"dislike":39,"score":-34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T03:14:16.000Z","msg":"正宗得個樣"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T03:16:56.000Z","msg":"意外壓傷致死都可以比你話"},{"pid":"1b62c167868a28842f57ae06efc2aae19f6742a4","tid":993484,"uid":54791,"like":20,"dislike":6,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"20553087d824ca53b29eef2ec3ab3ce9a6720d37","tid":993484,"uid":67500,"like":5,"dislike":39,"score":-34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T03:14:16.000Z","msg":"正宗得個樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T03:23:24.000Z","msg":"酸撚到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces